<p itemprop="description">A data architect designs and implements data solutions that meet business requirements. They work independently on complex data architecture challenges and provide guidance to junior team members.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Design comprehensive data architecture solutions for complex business requirements</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Create and maintain data models, data flows, and integration patterns</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead data governance initiatives and establish data standards</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Evaluate and recommend data technologies and platforms</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Collaborate with stakeholders to understand data requirements and constraints</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Mentor associate data architects and support their development</li>
    </ul>
</section>

